## 19. Common PingOne Error Codes

| Error | Cause | Resolution |
|---|---|---|
| `invalid_client` | Wrong credentials or wrong auth method | Use `CLIENT_SECRET_BASIC` (header), not body params alongside `code_verifier` |
| `invalid_grant` | Code already used, expired, or wrong `code_verifier` | Fresh PKCE per request; never reuse codes |
| `access_denied` | User denied, CIBA denied, or policy blocked | Surface to user; do not auto-retry |
| `authorization_pending` | CIBA user hasn't responded | Keep polling at specified interval |
| `slow_down` | Polling too fast | Increase CIBA interval by 5s (max 30s) |
| `expired_token` | CIBA `auth_req_id` expired | Start a new CIBA flow |
| `invalid_scope` | Scope not in PingOne resource grants | Add scope to app's resource grant in PingOne console |
| `invalid_redirect_uri` | URI not registered in app | Register exact URI in PingOne app settings |
| `interaction_required` | Session expired or MFA needed | Redirect to login with `acr_values` |
| `login_required` | `prompt=none` but no active session | Redirect to login without `prompt=none` |

